          even see a VISA that is in view. Whatever he sees,
          can be used against you. He can threaten you with
          whatever he recorded and can make your life as
          miserable as possible.
        </span>
        <a class="underline font-bold" style="color: #FF9912;" target="_blank" href="https://www.quora.com/Why-do-some-people-cover-their-laptop-cameras-with-tape-Is-it-just-paranoia">In this article</a>
